snippet.title: Final Rush Action Trailer
snippet.description:
http://steamcommunity.com/sharedfiles/filedetails/?id=114481455
Vote 'Yes' for Final Rush on Steam Greenlight if you want to play or support the game.

Final Rush is a Sci-Fi first person action shooter for the PC, built using the Unreal 3 Engine. It puts the players into the role of futuristic military police which take on dangerous jobs.

Please support continued development by pre-purchasing the game on IndieGoGo:
http://www.indiegogo.com/projects/final-rush/x/3798401

Or by mentioning us on Twitter and Facebook:
https://twitter.com/StrikeGames
http://www.facebook.com/pages/Strike-Games/103101993059040
